00:14:10.584 --> 00:14:12.476
Kalian semua!

00:14:52.119 --> 00:14:55.356
Hei, jangan menyerah!
Terus bertempur!

00:14:57.095 --> 00:14:58.847
Tidak mungkin bisa!

00:15:00.937 --> 00:15:02.355
Tinggalkan pos kalian!

00:15:02.443 --> 00:15:04.278
Semua kapal, berkumpul di sini!

00:15:14.392 --> 00:15:16.645
