00:16:02.960 --> 00:16:05.129
Aku juga akan membuat lubang
di tubuhmu!

00:16:08.947 --> 00:16:10.532
Aku akan mengusirmu dari sini!

00:16:12.051 --> 00:16:13.511
Rock 'n Roll...

00:16:15.447 --> 00:16:17.282
...Blaster!

00:16:41.130 --> 00:16:43.507
Wow!
Wakil Laksamana Doll!

00:16:43.864 --> 00:16:45.699
Dia petarung yang tangguh!
Sangat luar biasa!

00:16:45.933 --> 00:16:47.476
Kashii!

00:16:47.902 --> 00:16:50.913
